data.description: ***Sellers offering $10,000 towards buyer's closing costs/prepaids if contract executed prior to 2/4/2024*** Welcome home to one of the more spacious houses on the market in this beautiful Cypress Creek community!  This 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom, 2-story charmer boasts over 2700 square feet of well-designed living space.  Walk into the living room/dining combination area that is bathed in natural light through the windows and sliding doors that lead out to the covered patio and the back yard.  You’ll enjoy the gorgeous kitchen’s wooden 42” cabinets, cooking island, granite counters, pantry, and eat-in breakfast bar, and especially how it opens up into the roomy family room.  Head up the stairs to the open flexible loft area that can accommodate many uses.  Don’t miss the generously-sized primary bedroom suite, with its large walk-in closet and en suite bathroom that has dual sinks, a tub and a walk-in shower.  You’ll have plenty of space for family and guests with 4 additional nice-sized bedrooms (one of which is currently styled as an office).  You don’t have to walk far for the laundry room, and it is conveniently situated upstairs near the bedrooms.  The quarterly HOA fees are low.  You’ll have access to a beautiful community pool, recreation center, and sport courts.  Don't miss your chance to make his home yours! Schedule a showing today.
